name.k: Tsuro - The Game of the Path

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This gorgeous digital board game couldnt be any simpler to learn, but true mastery lies at the end of a long and winding path. As fans of Tsuros tabletop incarnation, we love how faithfullyand beautifullythe experience is re-created here. App-exclusive ways to play add new layers of depth, letting us get lost for hours among these tricky, twisty trails.
